room_title: Escape room "Movie Night" by XIT Escape Room in Orange Beach
room_address: 3800 Gulf Shores Pkwy #152 Gulf Shores, AL 36542
room_description: It is movie night for you and friends at a new house, a tradition that has been going on for 4 years. Just when you thought this would be the best movie night ever you are interrupted and told to get out before the serial killer friend of yours returns to the home you are in.
